'''Imperial machinists''' were specialized [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] that were trained to handle and maintain machines and vehicles such as [[HAVt B5 Juggernaut|Juggernauts]]. Some were stationed on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]], where a Juggernaut's [[drive shaft]] snapped. Once they requested replacement parts, they were often ignored and wouldn't receive them until after many days.

